<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="5" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[319,1716,985,1402]" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">
This species is distributed from Java and 
<collectingCountry box="[1183,1367,1258,1302]" name="Singapore" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">Singapore</collectingCountry>
to the 
<collectingCountry box="[1513,1716,1258,1302]" name="Philippines" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">Philippines</collectingCountry>
and northern 
<collectingCountry box="[569,743,1310,1352]" name="Australia" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">Australia</collectingCountry>
. It was not previously recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[1396,1506,1310,1352]" name="Guam" pageId="2" pageNumber="5">Guam</collectingCountry>
. We found it quite common and generally distributed.
</paragraph>
